Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:45.68,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing down the lighted path
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:53.08,Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}sorano mukó gawa made
